gtkmonop (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Release!
  * Fixed up tons of little bugs
  * Overhauled UI
  * Requires libgmonopd, can now start servers.

 -- Erik Bourget <ebourg@po-box.mcgill.ca>  Sun, 28 Oct 2001 14:13:13 -0500

gtkmonop (0.3-pre09032001) unstable; urgency=low

  * Overhauled pixmap loading/use, much more generic and 'nice' now
  * Transparency in pixmaps supported
  * Finished up 'gradient' theme, added to repository, made default for now
  * Double-buffered the board window, eliminated a lot of needless redraw
  * Fixed a few memory leaks
  * Redefined theme format a bit
  * Removed ugly GDK right-click hack, dunno why it works now :p

 -- Erik Bourget <ebourg@po-box.mcgill.ca>  Mon, 03 Sep 2001 18:53:26 -0400

